** @MS ( ERR MSG 53A)........3.........4.........5..>
ER01 INVALID DATE (KANBAN ISSUE DATE)
ER02 CUSTOMER NOT FOUND
ER03 CUSTOMER DETETED ALREADY
ER04 SELECT "1", "2", "3" OR "4"
ER05 KANBAN DATA NOT FOUND
ER06 LINE# SHOULD BE LESS THAN 13
ER07 END PAGE
ER08 ENTER LINE#
ER09 INVALID DATE (DELIVERY DATE)
ER10 INPUT '*' FOR NO COVER
